metadata.name: AstroBear #V2.1
metadata.description: AstroBear V2 is a collection of 1969 AstroBears with guns and goggles ready for take off made by the artist Rasmus Benjamin aka Creativesoul. Each of them is individually created, pushing the limits with a wide variety of RGB colors. Owners get a high res image of 6400x7980 pixels for prints up to 78.7 inches/2 meters in height. This NFT also holds a 19.6 inch/50 cm. IRL AstroBear sculpture. Check property to see if it has been claimed (yes/no) Claim your NFT in high resolution and the sculpture at: https://www.astrobearspace.club
